         <div class="full_bio"> 
          <p>I counsel regulated firms on using social media effectively while complying with industry rules and regulations. As Social Media and Compliance Specialist for Actiance, Inc., I am both an enthusiastic user of social media (follow me @belbey) and also led the development and delivery of more than 350 educational compliance programs per year for the Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (FINRA), a regulator for the securities industry. I’m located in Jersey City, overlooking Manhattan. At the intersection of social media and compliance, I am regularly quoted in industry publications such as Financial Planning,Corporate Compliance Insights, Compliance Week, Wealth Management, ClickZ, On Wall Street, Investment News, ProfNet, Pharmaceutical Compliance Monitor and Healthcare Risk Management. I also speak and live tweet (maybe too much!) at industry events.In addition to social media and compliance, I am passionate about films and filmmaking. My short film, "India: A Tourist's View" was an official selection for The Art of Brooklyn Film Festival and the Hoboken International Film Festival in 2014.</p> 
          <!-- ADD IF DATA CHECK --> 
